Install and configure CMake

Install MinGW-W64
- https://sourceforge.net/projects/mingw-w64/files/Toolchains%20targetting%20Win32/Personal%20Builds/mingw-builds/installer/mingw-w64-install.exe/download?use_mirror=deac-fra&download=&failedmirror=kumisystems.dl.sourceforge.net
- on the Settings page specify i686 Architecture
- choose default installation folder

Install GnuWin32
- zlib: download "Binaries" and "Developer files" zip-archives from http://gnuwin32.sourceforge.net/packages/zlib.htm and put them into C:\Program Files\GnuWin32
- pcre: download "Binaries" and "Developer files" zip-archives from http://gnuwin32.sourceforge.net/packages/pcre.htm and put them into C:\Program Files\GnuWin32

Build target bsdtar with i686-w64-mingw32 kit